<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="proportion-n">proportion <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prə'pɔːʃn/    美 /prə'pɔːrʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] 比例；比；[C] 部分；份额：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>proportion of</strong> boys to girls in our club is two to one.
我们俱乐部的男女比例是二比一。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 均衡；相称：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children have large eyes <strong>in proportion to</strong> their heads.
与脑袋相比，孩子们的眼睛显得很大。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="out-of-proportion-to">out of proportion to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>与…不成比例；和…不相称</strong>  </p></div>